text: Dora Honnywill was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 17 December 1870 and died on 18 March 1959. She competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Dora Honnywill == References == Category:1870 births Category:1959 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
